<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlḥạjẗ lyk wḥdk yạ rạʿynạ wsṭ ạlnạr wạlsẖwk btjynạ
 ntʿlq byk wtnjynạ wʿlsẖạnạ yạmạ bttḥml
 yạlly ḥbytnạ mn ạlạ̉wl bʿdnạ ʿnk ṭwl
 ạsẖtnạ nrjʿ lk tạny wbkẖlạṣk nfrḥ wnhll
