 nṭlb wjhk lyl wnhạr wlạ njry lgẖyrk ntswl
 ạlḥạjẗ lyk wḥdk yạ msyḥnạ ạnt ạlḥy mạlk ạ̉rwạḥnạ
 lạ ʿmr mkẖạftk tfạrqnạ wlạ mn gẖyr rwḥk hạnkml</lyrics>
